data.description: *MOTIVATED SELLER* Home appraised for $199,900 but seller is motivated!!!! Welcome to this well maintained 3 bedroom 3 bath home in great area, close to wooded forest preserve. Attractive covered porch leads you in.  All 3 bedrooms, hallway and large bright living room have hardwood floors. Main bedroom has private bath. Main bath has been updated with large walk in shower. Kitchen has plenty of counter space, breakfast bar, pantry and large eating area that leads to bright and sunny 3 seasons room. Lower level has large rec room with built ins.  Perfect for indoor entertaining. Large laundry room with plenty of space for storage or crafting. Bathroom with shower makes the lower level complete.  Extra large fenced in back yard with patio and side drive with a 2.5 car garage. Perfect area for outdoor enjoyment. Lots of storage space complete this great house!!!
